<div style="float:left; width:6em;text-align:left;">
<div class="noprint plainlinksneverexpand navbar" style="background:none; padding:0; font-weight:normal;;background: lightsteelblue; font-size: 90%;;border:none;; font-size:xx-small;"><a href="/wiki/Template:Campaignbox_Greco-Persian_Wars" title="Template:Campaignbox Greco-Persian Wars"><span title="View this template" style=";background: lightsteelblue; font-size: 90%;;border:none;">v</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="/w/index.php?title=Template_talk:Campaignbox_Greco-Persian_Wars&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Template talk:Campaignbox Greco-Persian Wars (page does not exist)"><span title="Discussion about this template" style=";background: lightsteelblue; font-size: 90%;;border:none;">d</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Campaignbox_Greco-Persian_Wars&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Campaignbox_Greco-Persian_Wars&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow"><span title="Edit this template" style=";background: lightsteelblue; font-size: 90%;;border:none;;">e</span></a></div>
</div>
<div style="padding: 0.2em 0; line-height: 1.3em;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><a href="/wiki/Greco%E2%80%93Persian_Wars" title="Greco–Persian Wars">Greco–Persian Wars</a></span></div>
