<li>Lloyd, Alan. <i>Marathon:The Crucial Battle That Created Western Democracy</i>. Souvenir Press, 2004. (<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/028563688X" class="internal">ISBN 0-285-63688-X</a>)</li>
